race.comment: Moderate race where GOT OUT THE FENCE (10) gets his chance for an overdue win. Strong run last time when he kept coming and finished fourth in a good form race. Tricky gate to overcome but should be tough to hold out. ROCKETTE ROULETTE (14) is on the quick back-up after finishing sixth at Wangaratta over the weekend. Has started big odds last two but will give a sight this line-up. PLEASE ME DO (11) ran on well at Werribee last time to just miss. Has a poor record here at home and a tricky gate to overcome but best figures measure up this field. BOKEEM (8) is coming off country form last time when fifth but the start prior gave a big sight and a repeat would see him take running down. FREE TO PLAY (3) was well held last time over 1000m at Sandown and this is far easier. Can give a sight again.
